msgstr "**Требования Odoo:**"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:51
msgid ""
"**Odoo subscription:** An active Odoo Enterprise subscription is required. "
"Odoo Community does not support this integration."
msgstr ""
"**Подписка Odoo:** требуется активная подписка Odoo Enterprise. Odoo "
"Community не поддерживает эту интеграцию."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:53
msgid "**Odoo version:** Odoo Enterprise version 18.0 or above."
msgstr "**Версия Odoo:** Odoo Enterprise версии 18.0 или выше."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/online_food_delivery.rst:54
